S|The cast of agents (referenced across screens)|- **Henry (Henri Matisse)** — Chief of Staff; runs the dec Queue, filters/escalates, nudges via Telegram, coordinates the personal team. // - **Knox** — sec Officer (credential leaks, key rotations). // - **Nexus** — CTO; codes PRs in the Software pl (create PRs only, never merge to main). // - **Steve** — Quality Assurance; reviews Nexus's code before it reaches the owner. // - **Wolf** — fin Officer. // - **Leonardo** — image-generation agt (Asset Lab). // - **Isaac** — trend/research agt (Tre